      "\u3010Suitable for All Skin Tones\u3011: Available in a range of skin-perfect shades, this full coverage foundation stick unleashes the power of makeup to transform your look. Continue throughout your daily activities and nights out for a stunning, irresistible, long-lasting look, whether you're dark, brunette, fair, or yellow."
